post.body:
I've made this account mainly for viewing ZeroMe on a bigger screen than my mobile phone, so may be meintioning it later will be quite useless.

And under no circumstances you should consider this account trustworthy.

@nofish: Good morning!
Fresh bugs for everyone!
On a given screenshot you can see 2 problems:
1) The app is called "ZeroNet clien" instead of "... clien**t**"
2) It's trying to access example.com that has a certificate problem. "selfsigned" if I am to translate from Russian.

@nofish: then I got this message. Not sure if it's still from ZeroNet, but the first one was, so I'm sending this one here too. I'll run some tests a bit later. (Kaspersky is veeery sloooow, so I can't even view the full report still)

It says that the web address that I try to access has a certificate problem "chain is not full" (my translation from Russian). And as soon as I close this message there is another one with another address, and all of them seem totally random. I cut all those connections, but messages never end...

---

Ah yes, the cert. is given by www.vt4nnkodp.net and it's cert. can't be checked.

---

After about 20-30 messages the flow has stopped. Yay!
Then I had *this* with my ZeroMe, but page reload has helped.
@ZAlex: Links "Windows", "Linux" and "Source" don't lead anywhere on your [PocketMod site](http://127.0.0.1:43110/1QGbEWp1Gex35kZAKuZmXfj455LhFBDDhg)
Sadly I can't read mentions to Musickiller here and mentions to Musickillerwork there.
It's funny when Steam is warning that some game is not to be played at work. As if any game is...
My boss came closer to my PC screen, so I've closed ZeroMe window. Too bad Steam was open too...

@nofish: as soon as I access ZeroID, it's trying to connect to some clearnet sites with seemingly random names. Kaspersky AV is telling that there are certificate problem with them.

example: www.yfnuymxsi.com

My solustion on "MS vs. Libre" problem is to use LibreOffice where I can and reformat documents to MS format in when I need to write any reports. Since I don't make large documents, it should be fine.

You know.. It's hard to really believe in God when none of people you talk to on daily basis, none of your close friends do believe even a bit. (well, there may be one, but we never talk about it)

However when a friend in a totally hopeless situation needs help, you pray, and sittuation is somewhat resolved an instant later... Well, you say it's a coincidence and don't really mention. Then it happens again. And again. And it becomes a seed of some grand idea, some hope.

Then everything lies in ruins (big thanks to the friend) and he makes a disastrous decision, you pray... for you don't even know what... pray till he's back online and it still works. Nothing in particular happens, which is good enough for a moment. He's alive which means there is still time.

Though somehow I feel tired. Not emotionally, not physicly... I just wish to stop asking for help and sort of meditate on the way things are.

A person with such a bright flare in his heart that all the world around seem to be a dark place.

*\- I don't hope for anything anymore.
\- Then I will hope for you.*

Day 100:
It's 3'rd September and it's 100 days left of this terrible dream called army. It's a holiday called "Сотка" [Sotka] (A Hundred). There is no particular celbration here, but spirits are high and we expect an easier time than we had before now. Good luck to us all. Let the last Hundred fly fast!

Day 99:
It's a hell of a morning and we expect even worse to come. Our bags and pockets were searched, items taken and many words spoken. Good news we are not some fools that will kick each other for that... Research Company we are after all... But hard times are ahead and God help us to have at least some free time next week.
